        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <ol class="visitor-benefits">
            <li>A Magic Code appears during Stingray programming.</li>
            <li>Viewers scan the code using their phone's camera.</li>
            <li>They access interactive formats (e.g., quiz, vote, offer, loyalty).</li>
            <li>Stingray earns from user actions and paid interactions.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="highlight">No technical integration beyond displaying the code is required.</p>
    </div>

